arStrings.szText:
{c_important}Caltrops{/c} and {c_important}Smoke Grenade{/c} receive your {c_important}Stun Grenade{/c} benefits and throw {c_important}Stun Grenades{/c} that deal {c_random}[(Owner.Weapon_Damage_Min_Total + Owner.Weapon_Damage_Delta_Total) * Affix_Value_1]{/c} Physical damage and Stun enemies for {c_number}[PowerTag.Rogue_Grenades."Script Formula 2"||]{/c} second.

Your {c_important}Stun Grenades{/c} deal {c_random}[Affix_Value_2|%|]{/c} increased damage.

{c_important}Caltrops{/c} and {c_important}Smoke Grenade{/c} throw {c_important}Stun Grenades{/c} that deal {c_random}[(Owner.Weapon_Damage_Min_Total + Owner.Weapon_Damage_Delta_Total) * Affix_Value_1]{/c} Physical damage and Stun enemies. {c_important}Stun Grenades{/c} do more damage.
